<L>__{interior kinograph studios (1931) zimmer's office day}
<D>__{music suddenly begins to play and we see feet dancing in another decor. except that from now on we actually hear the sound of the tap steps. we pull back to find peppy and george in zimmer's office. they're dancing for him. little by little, zimmer is convinced by them, and, when they finish their demonstration, he has a broad smile on his face.}
